[normal]Having established 
[normal]the fact that the Train Regulating and Controlling 
[normal]System can induce errors and contribute a collision hazard,
[normal] it is necessary to pay attention to the barriers that can prevent and protect the cyclist from this occupation hazard
[normal]. 
