[normal] 
[normal]a 
[normal]good indicator of safety performance whereas empirical data analysis does not show any kind of linear relationship
[normal]. Lack of Competence on the part of European Railway Agency in the application of System Thinking Approach to Safety 
[normal]as directed by EU Saf
[normal]ety Directive (2004/2009) 
[normal]is self –evident from the careful reading of the information listed on their website. 
[normal]Even UK HSE Reducing Risk and Protecting People suffers from this cognitive error
[normal]. 
