[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Application of Management Oversight and Risk Tree Worksheet as part of SIRI Framework to the Case Studies of Challenger Accident, Japanese Nuclear Accident, and Herefordshire Level Crossing Accidents show that dependability type of approach applied by auto
[normal]mation engineers and managers are not useful for identifying hazards and their elimination. 
[normal]The combination of latent failures in understanding has been listed in this accident case study as well. By correcting these level of safety may improve. 
